{"tid":1284151,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（全民健身）公海總 tg谷","createTime":"2019-07-04T04:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:35:41.000Z","uid":180114,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec0bd40c0882642f2e64d4f1a2e6b1e7cf86dd7","tid":1284151,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"依個tg谷盡量都唔好傾政治野<br />\n<br />\n黎得依個group都係想增強體能，力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我地冇場地既原因，主要會諗住係公園做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">義教</span>，其實主要教人街頭健身，教bodyweight動作<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論有關健身資訊，另外嚴重缺大量mentor，識基本動作就可以架啦，你地冇出黎野餐唔緊要 ，希望你地為香港出一分力，記住我地係唔收錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=ffa0c45a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NZ0BlxTpuh58PNn1sCyW0A</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各至努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb28604845addc1301e38c882851e41f2cec1c40","tid":1284151,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:57:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我無野講</span>"},{"pid":"f7df1f110105293cc356b328dca4bc2a737356e4","tid":1284151,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"窮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d704e9fab84e3ab3c871f024612cadb1c6d6042","tid":1284151,"uid":180114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280650</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係分化<br />\n<br />\n琴日有啲fd話依個post既樓主想單對單教<br />\n<br />\n但大家要知道  mentor&lt;participant<br />\n<br />\n所以根本冇可能實施到單對單教<br />\n<br />\n係公園做bodyweight training, 街頭健身更合乎效益，希望個位巴打唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n因為大家出發點都係為香港人好"},{"pid":"f740ef546837a298b87a6